Package org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.debug.core.jsdi.event

Interface Summary
BreakpointEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a breakpoint has been encountered.
DebuggerStatementEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a debugger; statement has been encountered.
Event Abstract description of a JSDI event
EventQueue A queue for JSDI EventSets
EventSet Describes a heterogeneous set of Events.
ExceptionEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating an exception has occurred.
LocatableEvent Description of a JSDI event that has a location
ScriptLoadEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a script has been loaded.
StepEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a stepping event occurred.
SuspendEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a suspend event occurred.
ThreadEnterEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a thread context has been entered.
ThreadExitEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a thread context has been exited.
VMDeathEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a VirtualMachine has been stopped in an unexpected way.
VMDisconnectEvent Description of a JSDI event indicating a VirtualMachine has been disconnected.
